divs: Sighting DetailsThough there may be reports of UFO having been witnessed passing through a solid object I haven't seen any. Generally, they are witnessed in the sky or bodies of water.Though the ones I tend to see are in the sky I wonder sometimes if the crafts have limitations. This sighting was of two ufo's that seemed to be avoiding hitting each other as they danced around like fire flys at high speeds, but intentionally avoided crashing into one another. There is, in my mind, a reason for this. See image. This a theroy only.
